title: Add reduce functions for FDTensor
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features

### PR changes
<!-- One of [ OPs | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
APIs

### Describe
1. Add 7 reduce functions for FDTensor: Max, Min, Sum, All, Any, Mean, Prod 
2. Add cpp unittests for 7 reduce functions. 
3. Add pull request template

#### Usage

```c++
FDTensor input, output;
std::vector<int> inputs = {2, 4, 3, 7, 1, 5};
input.SetExternalData({2, 3}, FDDataType::INT32, inputs.data());

// Calculate the max value for axis 0 of `inputs`
// The output result would be [[7, 4, 5]]
Max(input, &output, {0}, /* keep_dim = */true);

// Calculate the min value for axis 0 of `inputs`
// The output result would be [[2, 1, 3]]
Min(input, &output, {0}, true);

// Calculate the sum value for axis 0 of `inputs`
// The output result would be [[9, 5, 8]]
Sum(input, &output, {0}, true);

// Calculate the mean value for axis 0 of `inputs`
// The output result would be [[4, 2, 4]]
Mean(input, &output, {0}, true);

// Calculate the product value for axis 0 of `inputs`
// The output result would be [[14, 4, 15]]
Prod(input, &output, {0}, true);

std::array<bool, 6> bool_inputs = {false, false, true, true, false, true};
input.SetExternalData({2, 3}, FDDataType::BOOL, bool_inputs.data());

// Calculate the any value for axis 0 of `inputs`
// The output result would be [[true, false, true]]
Any(input, &output, {0}, true);

// Calculate the any value for axis 0 of `inputs`
// The output result would be [[false, false, true]]
All(input, &output, {0}, true);
```

Add Transpose function

### Usage

```c++
FDTensor input, output;
std::vector<float> inputs = {2, 4, 3, 7, 1, 5};
input.SetExternalData({2, 3}, FDDataType::FP32, inputs.data());

title: Optimize TensorRT backend to support rebuild engine
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
Function optimization

### PR changes
<!-- One of [ OPs | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
TensorRT Backend
### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
##### 优化TensorRT后端
- 当设定`UseTrtBackend`后，可不用手动设置`SetTrtInputShape`，而是改为在实际调用`Infer`接口时，根据输入的实际Shape进行Engine的build
- 当调用`Infer`时的输入数据Shape超过已经build的Engine范围，会重新进行Engine的构建，并重新序列化到本地
- 在加载序列化的TRT模型时，支持从模型中获取Shape范围

title: Add paddle quantize model support for ORT, TRT and MKLDNN deploy backend
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features

### PR changes
<!-- One of [ OPs | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
Others

### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Add paddle quantize model support for ORT, TRT and MKLDNN deploy backend

**ORT**
```
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_ort_backend()
option.set_model_path("yolov5s_new_format/model.pdmodel", "yolov5s_new_format/model.pdiparams")

#  设置量化模型的calibration路径，表示加载了paddle的量化模型
option.set_calibration_path("yolov5s_new_format/calibration_table.txt")

runtime = fd.Runtime(option)
data = np.random.rand(1, 3, 640, 640).astype("float32")
result = runtime.infer({"x2paddle_images":data})
```

**MKLDNN**
```
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_paddle_backend()
option.set_model_path("yolov5s_new_format/model.pdmodel", "yolov5s_new_format/model.pdiparams")

#  设置量化模型的calibration路径，表示加载了paddle的量化模型
option.set_calibration_path("yolov5s_new_format/calibration_table.txt")

runtime = fd.Runtime(option)
data = np.random.rand(1, 3, 640, 640).astype("float32")
result = runtime.infer({"x2paddle_images":data})
```

**ONNX-TRT**
```
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_trt_backend()
option.use_gpu()
option.set_model_path("yolov5s_new_format/model.pdmodel", "yolov5s_new_format/model.pdiparams")

#  设置量化模型的calibration路径，表示加载了paddle的量化模型
option.set_calibration_path("yolov5s_new_format/calibration_table.txt")
#  针对TRT，还需要指定TRT加载的量化cache表路径
option.set_trt_calibration_cache_path("yolov5s_new_format/calibration_cache.cache")

runtime = fd.Runtime(option)
data = np.random.rand(1, 3, 640, 640).astype("float32")
result = runtime.infer({"x2paddle_images":data})
```

### PR types
Others

### PR changes
Others

### Describe
1、添加ppcls benchmark脚本，共5个信息：Runtime、End2End、cpu_rss_mb、gpu_rss_mb以及gpu_util
2、cpu有三个backend：ORT、PDINFER以及OPENVINO，分为单线程以及多线程(thread_nums=8)
3、gpu包含四个：ORT、PDINFER、TRT以及TRT+fp16
4、将模型存储在```ppcls_model```目录，运行下列命令
```shell
sh run_benchmark_ppcls.sh

最终结果，gpu结果存在```struct_gpu_ppcls.txt```当中，cpu结果存在```struct_cpu_ppcls.txt```当中

```code

body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features
### PR changes
<!-- One of [ OPs | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
APIs
### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Add  uie python api

```python
import fastdeploy
import os

model_dir = "uie-base"
model_path = os.path.join(model_dir, "inference.pdmodel")
param_path = os.path.join(model_dir, "inference.pdiparams")
vocab_path = os.path.join(model_dir, "vocab.txt")

runtime_option = fastdeploy.RuntimeOption()
runtime_option.use_openvino_backend()

uie = fastdeploy.text.uie.UIEModel(
  model_path,
  param_path,
  vocab_path,
  position_prob=0.5,
  max_length=128,
  schema=['时间', '选手', '赛事名称'],
  runtime_option=runtime_option)

print(uie.predict(["2月8日上午北京冬奥会自由式滑雪女子大跳台决赛中中国选手谷爱凌以188.25分获得金牌！"]))
```

更新detection_result.md文档，增加实例分割mask属性说明 - 增加FDTensor::ExpandDim函数，用于升维操作 - C++/Python 推理后端测试情况 （该模型目前仅支持Paddle后端推理） | C++ Paddle-CPU | C++ Paddle-GPU |Python3.7 Paddle-CPU|Python3.7 Paddle-GPU| |:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:| |测试通过|测试通过|测试通过|不通过，cuBLAS报错| 因此，MaskRCNN的Python目前案例先跳过GPU推理，会回退到CPU推理。报错信息如下： ```bash -------------------------------------- C++ Traceback (most recent call last): -------------------------------------- 0 paddle::AnalysisPredictor::ZeroCopyRun() 1 paddle::framework::NaiveExecutor::Run() 2 paddle::framework::OperatorBase::Run(paddle::framework::Scope const&, phi::Place const&) 3 paddle::framework::OperatorWithKernel::RunImpl(paddle::framework::Scope const&, phi::Place const&) const 4 paddle::framework::OperatorWithKernel::RunImpl(paddle::framework::Scope const&, phi::Place const&, paddle::framework::RuntimeContext*) const 5 std::_Function_handler, paddle::operators::FCOpKernel, paddle::operators::FCOpKernel >::operator()(char const*, char const*, int) const::{lambda(paddle::framework::ExecutionContext const&)#1}>::_M_invoke(std::_Any_data const&, paddle::framework::ExecutionContext const&) 6 paddle::operators::FCOpKernel::Compute(paddle::framework::ExecutionContext const&) const 7 phi::funcs::FCFunctor::operator()(phi::GPUContext const&, int, int, int, float const*, float const*, float*, float const*, bool, bool) 8 void phi::funcs::Blas::GEMM(bool, bool, int, int, int, float, float const*, int, float const*, int, float, float*, int) const 9 phi::GPUContext::CublasCall(std::function const&) const 10 std::_Function_handler::GEMM(bool, bool, int, int, int, float, float const*, int, float const*, int, float, float*, int) const::{lambda(cublasContext*)#1}>::_M_invoke(std::_Any_data const&, cublasContext*&&) 11 phi::enforce::EnforceNotMet::EnforceNotMet(phi::ErrorSummary const&, char const*, int) 12 phi::enforce::GetCurrentTraceBackString[abi:cxx11](bool) ---------------------- Error Message Summary: ---------------------- ExternalError: CUBLAS error(15). [Hint: Please search for the error code(15) on website (https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/cublas/index.html#cublasstatus_t) to get Nvidia's official solution and advice about CUBLAS Error.] (at /build/Paddle/paddle/phi/kernels/funcs/blas/blas_impl.cu.h:35) [operator < fc > error] ``` - 可视化样例 - 补充 win11 + wsl2 + cuda 11.7 + cudnn 8.4 + trt 8.4 + python3.8 的尝试： 描述：尝试更换新的环境测试paddle-gpu + python推理，发现正常，不会出现cuBLAS错误，使用的是相同paddle inference预编译库，log如下： ```bash (py38) ➜ python git:(paddle_mask_rcnn) ✗ python ./infer_mask_rcnn.py --model_dir mask_rcnn_r50_1x_coco --image 000000014439.jpg --device gpu [INFO] csrc/fastdeploy/fastdeploy_runtime.cc(277)::Init Runtime initialized with Backend::PDINFER. title: Add paddle quantize model support for ORT, TRT and MKLDNN deploy backend
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features

### PR changes
<!-- One of [ OPs | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
Others

### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Add paddle quantize model support for ORT, TRT and MKLDNN deploy backend

Running a quantized model is the same as running a non-quantized model and calling the interface, without any special settings

**ORT**
```
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_ort_backend()
option.set_model_path("yolov5s_new_format/model.pdmodel", "yolov5s_new_format/model.pdiparams")

runtime = fd.Runtime(option)
data = np.random.rand(1, 3, 640, 640).astype("float32")
result = runtime.infer({"x2paddle_images":data})
```

**MKLDNN**
```
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_paddle_backend()
option.set_model_path("yolov5s_new_format/model.pdmodel", "yolov5s_new_format/model.pdiparams")

runtime = fd.Runtime(option)
data = np.random.rand(1, 3, 640, 640).astype("float32")
result = runtime.infer({"x2paddle_images":data})
```

**ONNX-TRT**
```
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_trt_backend()
option.use_gpu()
option.set_model_path("yolov5s_new_format/model.pdmodel", "yolov5s_new_format/model.pdiparams")

runtime = fd.Runtime(option)
data = np.random.rand(1, 3, 640, 640).astype("float32")
result = runtime.infer({"x2paddle_images":data})
```

title: Support build on jetson
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->

### PR changes
<!-- One of [ OPs | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->

### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->

支持FastDeploy在Jetson上的编译，当前仅支持ONNXRuntime CPU或TensorRT两种后端分别用于在CPU和GPU上的推理


如何在Jetson上编译，当打开开关`BUILD_ON_JETSON`时，会默认开启`ENABLE_ORT_BACKEND`和`ENABLE_TRT_BACKEND`

注意：FastDeploy在编译时会依赖第三方库`Eigen`，因此会自动拉取Gitlab上源码，如遇编译时拉取Eigen源码问题，可先使用如下命令配置git
```
git config --global http.sslverify false
```

编译前，需安装`patchelf`
```
sudo apt-get install patchelf
```

## Python Wheel
```
git clone https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/FastDeploy
cd FastDeploy/python
export BUILD_ON_JETSON=ON
export ENABLE_VISION=ON
python setup.py build
python setup.py bdist_wheel
```

执行完即会在`FastDeploy/python/dist`目录下生成wheel包文件，pip安装即可

## C++ SDK
```
git clone https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/FastDeploy
cd FastDeploy/python
mkdir build && cd build
cmake .. -DBUILD_ON_JETSON=ON -DENABLE_VISION=ON -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=${PWD}/fastdeploy_cpp_sdk
make -j8
make install
```
执行完后，`FastDeploy/build/fastdeploy_cpp_sdk`即为编译产出的C++部署库

title: Refine cpp/python api of visualize with lots of deprecated apis
body:
即将废弃API
## C++
`fastdeploy::vision::Visualize`结构体即将移除，与之相关如下函数同时移除
- `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::VisDetection`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy::vision::VisDetection`
- `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::VisSegmentation`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy::vision::VisSegmentation`
- `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::VisFaceDetection`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy::vision::VisFaceDetection`
- `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::VisOcr`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy::vision::VisOcr`
- `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::VisMattingAlpha`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy::vision::VisMatting`
- `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::SwapBackgroundSegmentation`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy::vision::SwapBackground` 
- `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::SwapBackgroundMatting`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy::vision::Visualize::SwapBackground`

## Python
- `fastdeploy.vision.swap_background_matting`废弃， 改为 `fastdeploy.vision.swap_background`
- `fastdeploy.vision.swap_background_segmentations`废弃， 改为 `astdeploy.vision.swap_background`

title: CVE-2007-4559 Patch
body:
# Patching CVE-2007-4559

Hi, we are security researchers from the Advanced Research Center at [Trellix](https://www.trellix.com). We have began a campaign to patch a widespread bug named CVE-2007-4559. CVE-2007-4559 is a 15 year old bug in the Python tarfile package. By using extract() or extractall() on a tarfile object without sanitizing input, a maliciously crafted .tar file could perform a directory path traversal attack. We found at least one unsantized extractall() in your codebase and are providing a patch for you via pull request. The patch essentially checks to see if all tarfile members will be extracted safely and throws an exception otherwise. We encourage you to use this patch or your own solution to secure against CVE-2007-4559. Further technical information about the vulnerability can be found in this [blog](https://www.trellix.com/en-us/about/newsroom/stories/research/tarfile-exploiting-the-world.html).

If you have further questions you may contact us through this projects lead researcher [Kasimir Schulz](mailto:kasimir.schulz@trellix.com).

### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->

Backend
Serving


### Describe
1. OpenVINO and Option support num_streams 
2. Runtime(PaddleBackend and OpenVINOBackend、TRTBackend) support Clone , ORT wait for the next PR
3. Serving create multiple Instances use Runtime*->Clone

Multiple Runtime Clone Example:
```
fastdeploy::Runtime runtime;
runtime.Init(runtime_option);

fastdeploy::Runtime runtime2;
runtime2.Init(runtime_option2);
```

Multiple Runtime NO Clone Example:
```
fastdeploy::Runtime runtime;
runtime.Init(runtime_option);

auto* runtime2 = runtime.Clone();
```

title: [Backend] OpenCV_CUDA preprocessors and PPClas preprocess optimization
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->
### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Backend

### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->

- Implemented OpenCV_CUDA preprocessors: BGR2RGB, ResizeByShort, CenterCrop, Normalize, NormalizeAndPermute, HWC2CHW
- Fuse preprocessors(BGR2RGB/RGB2BGR + Normalize + HWC2CHW).
- PPClas integrated OpenCV_CUDA preprocessing
- PPClas integrated preprocessors fusion
- PPClas end2end performance testing

### Experiment

PPClas, resnet50, 224x224, NV-P40/E5-2650
End2end test(preprocessing + inference + postprocessing)
Use INTER_LINEAR resizing
Latency in milliseconds
| Optimization\Image Size | 2560x1440 | 1920x1080 | 1280x720 | 640x480 |
|:--|:--|:--|:--|:--|
| Original | 9.72 | 8.42 | 6.24 | 5.40 |
| Reuse input&output tensors | 8.83 | 7.30 | 6.09 | 5.14 |
| Reuse input&output tensors and fuse BGR2RGB + Normalize + HWC2CHW | 5.48 | 5.36 | 4.67 | 4.37 |
| Reuse input&output tensors and fuse BGR2RGB + Normalize + HWC2CHW and OpenCV_CUDA | 6.12 | 5.26 | 4.33 | 3.89 |
| Reuse input&output tensors and fuse BGR2RGB + Normalize + HWC2CHW and OpenCV_CUDA with resize on CPU pinned memory | 4.91 | 4.36 | 4.35 | 4.11 |
| | 1.98x | 1.93x | 1.43x | 1.31x |

### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->

The title of this pull request should be `[PR type] Description of this pull request`, e.g `[Model] PP-Matting deployment support`    
  
PR的标题应该为 `[PR type] Description of this pull request`, 例如 `[Model] PP-Matting deployment support`  



### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
When we install TensorRT with the debian package, the related libraries are installed in `/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu` by default, so such users can pass `-DTRT_DIRECTORY=/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu` to complete compile and build.

title: [Bug Fix] fix camera preview size setting problem
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Bug Fix 

### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
- 优化摄像头分辨率调整逻辑，原有的逻辑会导致在小米10，小米12 pro等高分辨率的机型上无法适配到最合适的分辨率。该问题会导致人像分割模型（由于输入过高的分辨率，如1920，但模型的输入size是192或256）精度下降
- 已同步更新人像分割apk
- ppseg后处理优化，使用uint8 buffer而非fp32，性能对比(华为 nova 7, portrait_pp_humansegv2)：  

|uint8 buffer(优化后)|fp32 buffer(优化前)|模型推理固定耗时|  
|:---:|:---:|:---:|    
|6.63ms|9.997ms|4ms|

title: [Other]Refactor PaddleSeg with preprocessor && postprocessor && support batch
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Other
### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Refactor PaddleSeg with preprocessor && postprocessor && support batch

后处理逻辑说明：
PaddleSeg的develop分支[模型导出](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleSeg/blob/develop/docs/model_export_cn.md])共可以在末端添加三种输出算子，支持[argmax, softmax, none] 
1. argmax，输出类型为INT32/INT64，后处理流程：
``` CPP
 if(infer_result.shape != origin_input_shape){
   CreateUINT8MatFromInferResult
   ResizeMat
   ShareWithTensor(new_uint8_infer_result)
 } 
infer_result or new_uint8_infer_result -> SegmentationResult
```
2. none or softmax，输出类型为FP32，后处理流程：
``` CPP
 if(StoreScoreMap){
   Transpose(Infer_result, transform_Infer_result)
   if(ApplySoftmax){
     Softmax(transform_Infer_result, transform_Infer_result)
   }
 } else {
   Argmax(Infer_result, transform_Infer_result) 
 }
 if(infer_result.shape != origin_input_shape){
   CreateUINT8MatFromTransformInferResult or  CreateFP32MatFromInferResult
   ResizeMat
   ShareWithTensor(new_uint8_infer_result) or ShareWithTensor(infer_result)
 } 
if(StoreScoreMap){
  Argmax(transform_Infer_result, argmax_infer_result) 
  Max(transform_Infer_result, max_score_result)
  argmax_infer_result -> SegmentationResult.label_map
  max_score_result  -> SegmentationResult.score_map
} else {
   new_uint8_infer_result -> SegmentationResult
}
```
Fastdeploy SegModel 支持batch操作，基本原则是在preprocess阶段将batch中所有图片resize为batch中最大shape的图片
，后处理阶段再resize为原图大小

Fastdeploy(examples/vision/segmentation/paddleseg/python/infer.py) 与 PaddleSeg(deploy/python/infer.py)对比测试
显卡：Tesla V100
模型：portrait_pp_humansegv2_lite_256x144_inference_model (with argmax)
数据集：[mini_supervisely](https://paddleseg.bj.bcebos.com/humanseg/data/mini_supervisely.zip) 共351张图片
测试后端：Paddle Inference GPU
测试方法：Batch_Size为1，warmup 351张图片， 测试采用10个epoch，每个epoch 351张图片，算每张图片端到端平均推理时长
结果如下：

|           | 端到端平均推理时长（ms）(根据五次结果取平均)|
|:-----  |:----- |
| Fastdeploy | 40.64 |
| PaddleSeg(未对Mask结果resize回原图shape) | 63.97 |
| PaddleSeg(对Mask结果resize回原图shape) | 81.64 |

Batch 使用cityscapes数据集进行全量测试
Batch size 1
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16222477/203928321-13868d55-bb4f-4605-910f-94666625babe.png)
Batch size 5
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16222477/203928364-d7b34066-867d-4af2-afef-1f58e9c8907a.png)

title: [Functions] Add +-*/ operators and reshape for FDTensor
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Functions
### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Add +-*/ functions and operators for FDTensor

### Usage

#### Add function

```c++
#include "fastdeploy/function/elementwise.h"
......
FDTensor x, y, z;
x.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);
y.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);

// Use functions to get the result of x add y
Add(x, y, &z);

// Use operator to get the result of x add y
z = x + y;
```

#### Subtract function

```c++
#include "fastdeploy/function/elementwise.h"
......
FDTensor x, y, z;
x.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);
y.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);

// Use functions to get the result of x minus y
Subtract(x, y, &z);

// Use operator to  get the result of x minus y
z = x - y;
```

#### Multiply function

```c++
#include "fastdeploy/function/elementwise.h"
......
FDTensor x, y, z;
x.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);
y.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);

// Use functions to get the result of x multiply y
Multiply(x, y, &z);

// Use operator to  get the result of x multiply y
z = x * y;
```

#### Divide function

```c++
#include "fastdeploy/function/elementwise.h"
......
FDTensor x, y, z;
x.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);
y.Allocate({2, 3, 4}, FDDataType::FP32);

// Use functions to get the result of x divide y
Divide(x, y, &z);

// Use operator to  get the result of x divide y
z = x / y;
```

#### Reshape function

```c++
FDTensor x;
x.Allocate({ 2, 3, 4, 5 }, FDDataType::FP32);
x.Reshape({ -1, 3, 2, 2, 5 }); // new shape: { 2, 3, 2, 2, 5 }
x.Reshape({ 0, -1, 5, 2 }); // new shape: { 2, 6, 5, 2 }
```

### Describe
add poros directory to FastDeploy

Poros is an AI Inference Accelerator for deep learning framework. It can provide significantly lower inference latency comparing with original model, and provide much flexibility for dynamic graphs.
Poros mainly works on the TorchScript IR currently, that means it supports the models from PyTorch, ONNX, TensorFlow and any other framework that can be converted to TorchScript. also, we are planting to support more IRs in the future.
poros is designed to supports multiple hardware backends conveniently, For now, Poros supports GPU and XPU Device, It's welcomed to add additional devices.

title: [Backend] Support Intel GPU with heterogeneous mode
body:
## 英特尔集成显卡/独立显卡支持

通过OpenVINO后端支持集成显卡和独立显卡的支持

## 使用说明

通过以下方式启用
### Python
```
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_openvino_backend()
option.set_openvino_device(name="GPU")  # 使用独立或集成显卡
# option.set_openvino_device(name="GPU.1") # 如若同时存在集成和独立显卡，通过此方式使用独立显卡
```

### C++
```
fastdeploy::RuntimeOption option;
option.UseOpenVINOBackend();
option.SetOpenVINODevice("GPU");
// option.SetOpenVINODevice("GPU.1");
```

### GPU上推理问题

#### 1. 固定Shape

Intel GPU上部署要求模型Shape固定，因此在部署时，需要确保模型的输入Shape是固定的，例如在部署PaddleClas模型时，使用如下代码
```
import fastdeploy as fd
option = fd.RuntimeOption()
option.use_openvino_backend()
option.set_openvino_device("GPU")
# 原模型为[-1, 3, -1, -1]的输入，但实际部署时，每次进入的数据都为[1, 3, 224, 224]，通过此接口固定模型Shape
option.set_openvino_shape_info({"inputs": [1, 3, 224, 224]}) 

model_file = os.path.join(args.model, "inference.pdmodel")
params_file = os.path.join(args.model, "inference.pdiparams")
config_file = os.path.join(args.model, "inference_cls.yaml")
model = fd.vision.classification.PaddleClasModel(
    model_file, params_file, config_file, runtime_option=option)
```

#### 2.异构执行
Intel GPU上支持的算子数量与CPU并不一致，在部署PPYOLE时，如若全采用GPU执行，会出现如下提示
```
RuntimeError: Operation: multiclass_nms3_0.tmp_1 of type MulticlassNms(op::v0) is not supported
```

这是因为`MulticlassNMS`不被GPU支持，我们可以采取让这个算子在CPU上异构执行，来实现模型在GPU上的部署
```
    option = fd.RuntimeOption()
    option.use_openvino_backend()
    # 采用GPU和CPU异构执行方式
    option.set_openvino_device("HETERO:GPU,CPU")
    # 固定输入Shape
    option.set_openvino_shape_info({"image":[1,3,640,640], "scale_factor":[1,2]})
   # 设置CPU上算子
    option.set_openvino_cpu_operators(["MulticlassNms"])

    model = fd.vision.detection.PPYOLOE(
      model_file, params_file, config_file, runtime_option=option)
```

title: [osx] detect cross compiling architecture
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
Other: Building

### Describe
macOS 的工具链支持 arm64 和 x86_64 的交叉编译，可以通过把 `CMAKE_OSX_ARCHITECTURES` 设置为 `arm64` 或 `x86_64` 来设置。

目前的构建脚本下载预编译库时，固定使用了 `CMAKE_HOST_SYSTEM_PROCESSOR`。

为了能比较灵活地进行交叉编译，此 PR 针对 macOS 平台添加了辅助函数 `get_osx_architecture()` 和变量 `CURRENT_OSX_ARCH` 来方便下载对应的依赖库。

P.S. 如果可以的话，希望未来可以添加 universal 版的预编译库。

title: [Other] Add Model Clone function for PaddleClas && PaddleDet && PaddleSeg
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Other
### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
> Multiple PaddleClas NO Clone Example:
> 
> ```
> auto model = fastdeploy::vision::classification::PaddleClasModel(model_file, params_file, config_file, option);
> 
> auto model2 = fastdeploy::vision::classification::PaddleClasModel( model_file, params_file, config_file, option);
> 
> ```
> 
> Multiple PaddleClas Clone Example:
> 
> ```
> auto model = fastdeploy::vision::classification::PaddleClasModel(model_file, params_file, config_file, option);
> 
>auto model2 = model.Clone();
> ```

硬件：Intel(R) Xeon(R) Gold 6271C CPU @ 2.60GHz  
模型：ResNet50_vd_infer
后端：CPU OPENVINO后端

单进程内初始化多个模型，内存占用
| 模型数 | model.Clone()后 | Clone后model->predict()后    | 不Clone模型初始化后| 不Clone后model->predict()后 |
|:--- |:----- |:----- |:----- |:----- |
|1|322M |325M |322M|325M|
|2|322M|325M|559M|560M|
|3|322M|325M|771M|771M|

模型多线程预测内存占用
| 线程数 | model.Clone()后 | Clone后model->predict()后    | 不Clone模型初始化后| 不Clone后model->predict()后 |
|:--- |:----- |:----- |:----- |:----- |
|1|322M |337M |322M|337M|
|2|322M|343M|548M|566M|
|3|322M|347M|752M|784M|

title: [ARM] fix VisSegmentation background error with bit ops
body: ### PR types(PR类型) Bug Fix ### Description - 增加neon向量化位运算，实现对于label为0的mask，保留原始图片的像素值。原来的可视化函数，对于label为0的区域，绘制mask之后会导致图像整体变暗。（同步修复了原始的纯C++实现） - 可视化效果：mask权重0.8，原来的方式会整体变暗 |原图|优化前|优化后| |:---:|:---:|:---:| |![portrait_heng](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31974251/206896088-28c547b0-0b12-43d4-bf05-1f2d158ffbe0.jpg)|![ppseg_vis_result_fast_08](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31974251/206896103-087f3561-d545-4233-8300-443c4acd4b29.jpg)|![ppseg_vis_result_fast_08_bg](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31974251/206896122-e8724556-ce17-4b1e-b6af-ce4e61635d39.jpg)| - 性能：小米 12 pro - 单线程：1.01 ms -> 1.05ms - OMP双线程：0.65 ms -> 0.72ms

body: 说明：此超分算法UI用到了Subsampling Scale Image View，此控件用来显示大型图像，同时允许放大高分辨率细节，最高支持20k分辨率的图片显示，但较大的图像速度较慢，控件链接：https://github.com/davemorrissey/subsampling-scale-image-view ![infoflow_2022-12-14_18-19-47](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14995488/207569375-4847f3e7-f491-49e0-9375-70f2b3288f2f.png) 1、点击开始按钮，进入超分算法： 2、点击拍照或从相册选择图片（这里为了实现效果暂时写死了图片）： 3、进入图片对比页面： 4、在开始运行前，要先选择放大倍数： 5、选择要放大的倍数： 6、点击开始后显示结果图： 7、对上下图片进行缩放移动可以来对比图片细节： 8、点击复位按钮可以将图片缩放到初始位置（倍率不变）： ------------------------------------------下面是补充------------------------------------------------------------ 9、删除实时识别相机页面，在对比页添加相册选择按钮： 10、选择一张图片后返回详情页： 11、选择倍率点击开始后显示结果（这里并没有做具体实现，先展示效果，其他功能同上）：

title: [FDTensor] Add device id to output tensor
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
FDTensor
### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
修改输出Tensor的device id。输出的Tensor默认device id为-1。当将输出Tensor转化dlpack格式时，其device id为-1，会影响from_dlpack将其反序列化。例如Paddle，会在该DLTensor对应的device id设备上创建一块显存，再将其数据拷贝到新建显存中。但由于device id为-1，在创建显存时就会马上失败。

title: [Model] Add YOLOv5-seg
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Model

### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
- Add YOLOv5-seg Model
- Move Mask data dtype from int32_t to uint8_t
- Add round() the box in advance when taking the mask size
- related https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/FastDeploy/issues/917

### Benchmark测试

#### 环境
CPU: Intel(R) Xeon(R) Gold 6271C CPU @ 2.60GHz
GPU：T4
CUDA：11.7
Cudnn：8.4
Python：3.7
TensorRT：8.4.3.1

#### 结果
共1000次测速，前200次warmup

原repo：
| backend | thread nums | run time(ms) | e2e time(ms) |
| -----------------| ---------- | -------------- | ----- |
| ORT_CPU | 8 | 60.93  | 71.96  |
| ORT_GPU | - | 19.74 | 30.95  |

FastDeploy：
| backend      | thread nums   | run time(ms) | e2e time(ms) |
| -----------------| ---------- | -------------- | ----- |
| ORT_CPU | 8 | 50.23  | 71.49 |
| OV_CPU | 8 | 40.28  | 61.67  |
| ORT_GPU | - | 20.59 | 41.53  |
| ONNX-TRT | - | 14.56  | 35.73 |
| ONNX-TRT FP16 | - | 7.82 | 28.94 |

#### 差距原因
差距主要在Mask的后处理耗时上：

后处理主要分为：NMS + MatMul + Sigmoid + Resize

原repo在处理Mask上，因为为torch.Tensor，MatMul + Sigmoid + Resize一共耗时5～6ms左右

FD因为FDTensor无MatMul等OP，需转成cv::Mat进行处理，且每张图都需要Resize回原图，具体耗时如下：

MatMul：11.5ms
Sigmoid + Resize：4ms(eg：如果有22个框，每个框里的Mask都需要resize回原图)

#### 解决方案
- 方案一：新增FDTensor OP：MatMul，Sigmoid以及Resize
- 方案二：采用phi算子库

title: [Android] support fastdeploy build with static deps(60Mb->29~31Mb)
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Android

### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
- [x] 支持FastDeploy Android库静态链接所有依赖库（opencv、flycv、paddle lite）, 最终可获得不依赖第三方库的libfastdeploy.so
- [x] 增加fastdeploy_jni.cmake支持编译主库时联编JNI so库（-DWITH_JAVA=ON）
- [x] FastDeploy Android C++库体积优化：60Mb->29~31Mb（arm64-v8a: 17-18Mb, armeabi-v7a: 12-13Mb）

|架构|优先前|优化后|优化后编译aar或app需要的库|优化后最终编译后aar依赖的库|     
|---|---|---|---|---|      
|arm64-v8a| libfastdeploy.so(3.4Mb), libflycv_shared.so(1.5Mb), libopencv_java4.so(17Mb), libpaddle_full_api_shared.so(15Mb), 共37Mb | libfastdeploy.so(17-18Mb，只包含runtime时为14Mb) |  libfastdeploy.so + opencv静态库（fd的预测接口目前显式地使用了opencv api）|  libfastdeploy.so(17-18Mb) |       
|armeabi-v7a| libfastdeploy.so(3.5Mb), libflycv_shared.so(1.0Mb), libopencv_java4.so(11Mb), libpaddle_full_api_shared.so(7Mb), 共22.5Mb | libfastdeploy.so(12-13Mb) |  libfastdeploy.so + opencv静态库（fd的预测接口目前显式地使用了opencv api）|  libfastdeploy.so(12-13Mb) |       

- [x] 支持编译FastDeploy静态库（通过动态库的dependency tree来获取所有的静态依赖库并打包合并）：libfastdeploy_static.a (测试成功)  

```bash
(py38) ➜  arm64-v8a git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ du -sh *
 18M	libfastdeploy.so
216M	libfastdeploy_static.a
(py38) ➜  arm64-v8a git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ readelf -d libfastdeploy.so | grep NEEDED
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [liblog.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libandroid.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libc.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libz.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libdl.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libm.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libmediandk.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libc++_shared.so]
```
- [x] c++ 动态库case测试，测试paddle yolov8n，结果正常。
- [x] c++ 静态库case测试，测试paddle yolov8n，结果正常。

![vis_result](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31974251/214243767-fe54215f-4667-4273-932a-2b9f5ad3eb39.jpg)  

编译出的可执行文件无任何非系统库依赖，也不依赖fastdeploy.  
```bash
(py38) ➜  build readelf -d infer_ppyolov8_demo | grep NEEDED
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)          Shared library: [liblog.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)          Shared library: [libm.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)          Shared library: [libc++_shared.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)          Shared library: [libdl.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)          Shared library: [libc.so]
```

- [x] aar库体积优化：基于FastDeploy静态库或联编的libfastdeploy_jni.so，理论上两种方式的效果一样。基于FastDeploy静态库的方式较为方便  

arm64-v8a(7Mb)及armeabi-v7a(5Mb)双架构aar库总体积12Mb（优化前23Mb）
```bash
BUILD SUCCESSFUL in 20s
29 actionable tasks: 10 executed, 19 up-to-date
[INFO] --- Built java aar package!
total 26632
-rw-r--r--  1 qiuyanjun  staff    12M  1 24 21:02 fastdeploy-debug.aar
```
库依赖分析：对aar进行拆包分析，可见编译后的aar库中，已经不依赖fastdeploy，只依赖Android的系统库。
```bash
  creating: jni/arm64-v8a/
  inflating: jni/arm64-v8a/libc++_shared.so  
  inflating: jni/arm64-v8a/libfastdeploy_jni.so  
   creating: jni/armeabi-v7a/
  inflating: jni/armeabi-v7a/libc++_shared.so  
  inflating: jni/armeabi-v7a/libfastdeploy_jni.so  
   creating: arm64-v8a/
   creating: armeabi-v7a/
(py38) ➜  aar git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ ls
AndroidManifest.xml  R.txt                armeabi-v7a          fastdeploy-debug.aar jni
META-INF             arm64-v8a            classes.jar          fastdeploy-debug.zip proguard.txt
(py38) ➜  aar git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ cd jni                                       
(py38) ➜  jni git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ ls
arm64-v8a   armeabi-v7a
(py38) ➜  jni git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ du -sh * 
 19M    arm64-v8a
 13M    armeabi-v7a
(py38) ➜  jni git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ cd arm64-v8a         
(py38) ➜  arm64-v8a git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ du -sh * 
1004K   libc++_shared.so
 18M    libfastdeploy_jni.so
arm64-v8a git:(support_fd_android_staticlib) ✗ readelf -d libfastdeploy_jni.so | grep NEEDED
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libjnigraphics.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [liblog.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libGLESv2.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libEGL.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libm.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libc++_shared.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libdl.so]
  0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)       Shared library: [libc.so]
```

- [x] Android app 测试 
   - [x] 基于fastdeploy静态库+aar编译app
   - [x] 运行app 

app编译log:
```bash
BUILD SUCCESSFUL in 1m 8s
49 actionable tasks: 49 executed
[INFO] --- Built FastDeploy Android app.
```
app运行log:
```bash
2023-01-24 21:23:50.807 4340-4422/com.baidu.paddle.fastdeploy.app.examples D/[FastDeploy][JNI]: Avg runtime costs 7.914773 ms
2023-01-24 21:23:50.807 4340-4422/com.baidu.paddle.fastdeploy.app.examples D/[FastDeploy][JNI]: [End] Release SegmentationResult & CxxBuffer in native !
2023-01-24 21:23:50.842 4340-4422/com.baidu.paddle.fastdeploy.app.examples D/[FastDeploy][JNI]: Predict from native costs 8.540000 ms
2023-01-24 21:23:50.842 4340-4422/com.baidu.paddle.fastdeploy.app.examples D/[FastDeploy][JNI]: Avg runtime costs 7.914375 ms
2023-01-24 21:23:50.842 4340-4422/com.baidu.paddle.fastdeploy.app.examples D/[FastDeploy][JNI]: [End] Release SegmentationResult & CxxBuffer in native !
2023-01-24 21:23:50.881 4340-4422/com.baidu.paddle.fastdeploy.app.examples D/[FastDeploy][JNI]: Predict from native costs 7.512001 ms
2023-01-24 21:23:50.881 4340-4422/com.baidu.paddle.fastdeploy.app.examples D/[FastDeploy][JNI]: Avg runtime costs 7.911790 ms
```

- 修改较多，是否暂不合入？后续继续review，以确认是整个PR合入，还是拆分成不同PR。  
- 备注：进一步的优化思路 -> 由于使用full api, with_extra ops，因此lite库体积比没有编译with_extra的库要大。进一步的fd库体积优化，可以考虑对在编译时**对lite extra ops进行op级别的裁剪**，只选择部分extra ops，而不是所有extra ops，参考 [lite/operators/CMakeLists.txt](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle-Lite/blob/develop/lite/operators/CMakeLists.txt). 该项优化只能针对**特定的模型集合**，对于android armv8，大约还有3~5Mb左右的库体积优化空间（即FD使用只使用包含部分extra ops的lite库）。

title: [Backend] support bechmark mode for runtime and backend
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Backend  

### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->  
- 增加benchmark模式，通过-DENABLE_BENCHMARK=ON开启
  - [x] 支持统计不带H2D和D2H的纯推理引擎耗时  
  - [x] 支持benchmark模式下，取消各个模型hardcode的xxx_valid_backends限制 
  - [x] 增加对应的pybind接口，支持python benchmark测试
  - [x] 各个推理后端测试：已测试ort, ov, trt, paddle-mkldnn, paddle-trt，已在相同的机器上和ppclas测的ov性能对齐 

用法：
- 给一个推理后端增加profile功能的示例：只需要在infer前后增加两个宏。
```c++
// OpenVINOBackend::Infer 
RUNTIME_PROFILE_LOOP_H2D_D2H_BEGIN
// do something .... 
RUNTIME_PROFILE_LOOP_BEGIN(1)
// The codes which wrapped by 'BEGIN(1) ~ END' scope 
// will only run once when profiling mode is not enabled.
request_.infer();  
RUNTIME_PROFILE_LOOP_END
// do something .... 
RUNTIME_PROFILE_LOOP_H2D_D2H_END
```
- 开启profile功能的示例

```python
option.enable_profiling(include_h2d_d2h=False, repeat=5000, warmup=10)
model = fd.vision.classification.PaddleClasModel(
            model_file, params_file, config_file, runtime_option=option)
result = model.predict(im_ori)  # will run at profile mode
profile_time = model.get_profile_time()
```
- log:
```bash
python benchmark_ppcls.py --model MobileNetV1_x0_25_infer --image ILSVRC2012_val_00000010.jpeg --cpu_num_thread 10 --repeat 5000 --warmup 10 --backend ov --profile_mode runtime --include_h2d_d2h False

Runtime(ms): 0.6852001999999999

body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->

Other
### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Add c sharp api for fastdeploy
### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
1. Add c sharp api for fastdeploy. We expose api like C++ to users, and call underlying c api to implement functions.

TestCode Demo:
```C#
// Copyright (c) 2023 PaddlePaddle Authors. All Rights Reserved.
//
// Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the "License");
// you may not use this file except in compliance with the License.
// You may obtain a copy of the License at
//
//     http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
//
// Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software
// distributed under the License is distributed on an "AS IS" BASIS,
// WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.
// See the License for the specific language governing permissions and
// limitations under the License.

using System;
using System.IO;
using System.Runtime.InteropServices;
using OpenCvSharp;
using fastdeploy;

namespace Test
{
    public class TestPPYOLOE
    {
        public static void Main(string[] args)
        {
            if (args.Length < 3) {
                Console.WriteLine(
                    "Usage: infer_demo path/to/model_dir path/to/image run_option, " +
                    "e.g ./infer_model ./ppyolo_dirname ./test.jpeg 0"
                );
                Console.WriteLine( "The data type of run_option is int, 0: run with cpu; 1: run with gpu");
                return;
            }
            string model_dir = args[0];
            string image_path = args[1];
            string model_file = model_dir + "\\" + "model.pdmodel";
            string params_file = model_dir + "\\" + "model.pdiparams";
            string config_file = model_dir + "\\" + "infer_cfg.yml";
            RuntimeOption runtimeoption = new RuntimeOption();
            int device_option = Int32.Parse(args[2]);
            if(device_option==0){
                runtimeoption.UseCpu();
            }else{
                runtimeoption.UseGpu();
            }
            vision.detection.PPYOLOE model = new vision.detection.PPYOLOE(model_file, params_file, config_file, runtimeoption, ModelFormat.PADDLE);
            Mat image = Cv2.ImRead(image_path);
            vision.DetectionResult res = model.Predict(image);
            Mat res_img = vision.Visualize.VisDetection(image, res, 0, 1, 0.5f);
            Cv2.ImShow("result.png", res_img);
            Cv2.WaitKey(0);

        }

    }
}
```

title: [Other] Enable to hidden INFO/WARNING log informations
body:
### 增加关闭FD日志接口

FD中由`FDINFO`/`FDWARNING`/`FDERROR`分别输出提示性日志、警告性日志和错误日志，此PR中提供接口关闭或打开`FDINFO`/`FDWARNING`的输出日志。关联issue https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/FastDeploy/issues/1364 https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/FastDeploy/issues/252

#### C++函数
```
void fastdeploy::SetLogger(bool enable_info = true, bool enable_warning = true);
```
使用示例
```
fastdeploy::SetLogger(false); // 关闭INFO日志，建议保留WARNING日志
```

#### Python函数
```
def set_logger(enable_info=True, enable_warning=True)
```
使用示例
```
import fastdeploy as fd
fd.set_logger(enable_info=False) # 关闭INFO日志，建议保留WARNING日志
```

title: [Shell] Support fastdeploy_init.sh script for ZSH terminal
body:
### Other

### Description
脚本在 sh bash 中工作正常，但是某些行在 zsh 中不支持。

本PR
1. 优化对zsh的支持
   * BASH_SOURCE支持默认值 "." 
   * FASTDEPLOY_LIBRARY_PATH 展开为绝对路径
   * ALL_SO_FILES ALL_DYLIB_FILES 在zsh 与 bash的区别处理. zsh 需要用小括号变成数组, bash能够自动识别为数组

3. 增强健壮性。
   对新LD_LIBRARY_PATH进行去重处理，避免多次运行 source ./fastdeploy_init.sh 导致 LD_LIBRARY_PATH 里面大量重复

title: [Benchmark] Add pure runtime benchmark bin
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->

### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->

- 支持任意模型runtime benchmark  

单输入示例：
```bash
./benchmark --model ResNet50_vd_infer --config_path config/config.x86.ov.fp32.txt --shapes 1,3,224,224 --names inputs --dtypes FP32
```  
多输入示例：  
```bash 
./benchmark --model yolov5_s_300e_coco --config_path config/config.arm.lite.fp32.txt --shapes 1,3,640,640:1,2 --names image:scale_factor --dtypes FP32:FP32
```
Paddle-TRT示例 ：
```bash  
./benchmark --model ResNet50_vd_infer --config_path config/config.gpu.paddle_trt.fp16.txt --trt_shapes 1,3,224,224:1,3,224,224:1,3,224,224 --names inputs --dtypes FP32
```
支持FD全部后端和全部模型格式：--model_file, --params_file(optional), --model_format
```bash
# ONNX模型示例
./benchmark --model ResNet50_vd_infer --model_file inference.onnx --model_format ONNX --config_path config/config.gpu.trt.fp16.txt --trt_shapes 1,3,224,224:1,3,224,224:1,3,224,224 --names inputs --dtypes FP32
```
统计内显存占用：--mem 或 在config.txt中指定  
```bash
./benchmark --mem --model ResNet50_vd_infer --config_path config/config.x86.ov.fp32.txt --shapes 1,3,224,224 --names inputs --dtypes FP32
```
推理并dump 输出 tensor用作对比： --dump
```bash 
./benchmark --dump --model ResNet50_vd_infer --config_path config/config.x86.ov.fp32.txt --shapes 1,3,224,224 --names inputs --dtypes FP32
```
对比两个 dumped 的tensor :  --diff 
```bash
./benchmark --diff --tensors ov_linear_77.tmp_1.txt:lite_linear_77.tmp_1.txt
```
显示模型的输入信息： --info
```bash
./benchmark --info --model picodet_l_640_coco_lcnet --config_path config/config.arm.lite.fp32.txt 
```

title: [CVCUDA] Add CV-CUDA support in PaddleSeg
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
CVCUDA
### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
#### 改动
- PaddleSegPreprocessor继承ProcessorManager
- 移除PaddleSegPreprocessor::Run()
- 实现PaddleSegPreprocessor::Apply()
- 支持开启CVCUDA

#### 性能测试

CPU: Intel(R) Xeon(R) Gold 6271C CPU @ 2.60GHz
GPU: T4
Model:

- https://bj.bcebos.com/paddlehub/fastdeploy/PP_LiteSeg_B_STDC2_cityscapes_without_argmax_infer.tgz
Batchsize: 4
Input image shapes:

```
  std::vector<cv::Mat> imgs;
  cv::resize(im, im, cv::Size(1920, 1080));
  imgs.push_back(im);
  cv::resize(im, im, cv::Size(1080, 1920));
  imgs.push_back(im);
  cv::resize(im, im, cv::Size(354, 260));
  imgs.push_back(im);
  cv::resize(im, im, cv::Size(780, 450));
  imgs.push_back(im);
```

Backend: ORT CPU/GPU
Warmup 100 rounds，tested 1000 rounds and get avg. latency.

Processor|OpenCV|CV-CUDA
------|:-------:|--------:
preprocess cost|234.50ms|12.22ms
end2end cost|1.16s|1.06s

title: bug fix: 修复contrib中的det模型后处理在遇到没有检测框的图时导致同batch中接下来的图片结果全部为空的bug
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
bug fix
### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
在`fastdeploy/vision/detection/contrib/yolov8/postprocessor.cc`中95行
```c++
if ((*results)[bs].boxes.size() == 0) {
      return true;
}
```
会导致如果同一个batch中有检测结果为空的图片那么接下来的图片的检测结果就不再处理。将`return true;` 替换为`continue;`避免此问题。

其他contrib中的postprocessor也有同样的问题。

title: Fix inconsistency when boxes is empty by inserting full ROI
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/pull/24810 -->


### PR types(PR类型)
<!-- One of PR types [ Model | Backend | Serving | Quantization | Doc | Bug Fix | Other] -->
Bug Fix

### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
When `boxes` is empty, the full-size image is used as the inference input. However, the corresponding full ROI was not inserted into `boxes`, leading to a mismatch where `boxes.size() == 0` but `text.size() == 1`.
This behavior is inconsistent with the design documented, which specifies that `boxes` and `text` should always have the same number of elements.
This PR fixes the issue by properly inserting the full ROI into boxes.

FastDeploy 2.0: Large Language Model Deployment
body:
## News
 🔥 Released FastDeploy v2.0: Supports inference and deployment for ERNIE 4.5. Furthermore, we open-source an industrial-grade PD disaggregation with context caching, dynamic role switching for effective resource utilization to further enhance inference performance for MoE models.

## About
FastDeploy is an inference and deployment toolkit for large language models and visual language models based on PaddlePaddle. It delivers production-ready, out-of-the-box deployment solutions with core acceleration technologies:
* 🚀 Load-Balanced PD Disaggregation: Industrial-grade solution featuring context caching and dynamic instance role switching. Optimizes resource utilization while balancing SLO compliance and throughput.
* 🔄 Unified KV Cache Transmission: Lightweight high-performance transport library with intelligent NVLink/RDMA selection.
* 🤝 OpenAI API Server and vLLM Compatible: One-command deployment with https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/ interface compatibility.
* 🧮 Comprehensive Quantization Format Support: W8A16, W8A8, W4A16, W4A8, W2A16, FP8, and more.
* ⏩ Advanced Acceleration Techniques: Speculative decoding, Multi-Token Prediction (MTP) and Chunked Prefill.
* 🖥️ Multi-Hardware Support: NVIDIA GPU, Kunlunxin XPU, Hygon DCU, Ascend NPU, Iluvatar GPU, Enflame GCU, MetaX GPU etc.

## Get Started
Learn how to use FastDeploy through our documentation:
* https://console.cloud.baidu-int.com/devops/icode/repos/baidu/paddle_internal/FastDeploy/blob/feature%2Finference-refactor-20250528/docs/get_started/quick_start.md
* https://console.cloud.baidu-int.com/devops/icode/repos/baidu/paddle_internal/FastDeploy/blob/feature%2Finference-refactor-20250528/docs/get_started/ernie-4.5.md
* https://console.cloud.baidu-int.com/devops/icode/repos/baidu/paddle_internal/FastDeploy/blob/feature%2Finference-refactor-20250528/docs/get_started/ernie-4.5-vl.md
* https://console.cloud.baidu-int.com/devops/icode/repos/baidu/paddle_internal/FastDeploy/blob/feature%2Finference-refactor-20250528/docs/offline_inference.md

* https://console.cloud.baidu-int.com/devops/icode/repos/baidu/paddle_internal/FastDeploy/blob/feature%2Finference-refactor-20250528/docs/supported_models.md

## Supported Models

|ERNIE-4.5-300B-A47B-Base| BF16/WINT4/WINT8 | ✅（WINT4/Expert Parallelism)| ✅ | ✅|✅(WINT4)| ❌ | 128K |

title: Feat/blackwell sm100 support
body:
This change integrates specific, expert-provided CUTLASS heuristic
configurations for the NVIDIA Blackwell (SM100) GPU architecture,
replacing previous placeholders. This includes:

- Updated `custom_ops/gpu_ops/cutlass_extensions/gemm_configs.h`:
    - Populated `CutlassTileConfigSM100` enum with specific tile shapes
      (e.g., CtaShape64x64x128B, CtaShape128x128x128B) suitable for SM100.
    - Added `FP4_ONLY` to `CandidateConfigTypeParam` for new FP4 paths.

- Updated `custom_ops/gpu_ops/cutlass_kernels/cutlass_heuristic.cu`:
    - Implemented `get_candidate_tiles_sm100` with detailed logic for
      selecting tile configurations based on GROUPED_GEMM and FP4_ONLY flags,
      using the new SM100 tile enums.
    - Implemented `supports_mcast_along_m_sm100` and
      `supports_mcast_along_n_sm100` with specific tile checks for Blackwell.
    - Updated the `sm == 100` (Blackwell) block in `get_candidate_configs`
      to use these new helper functions and accurately populate candidate
      kernel configurations for various cluster shapes.

- `custom_ops/setup_ops.py` remains configured to compile for
  `arch=compute_100a,code=sm_100a` with CUDA 12.9+ for these features.

This aligns the codebase with heuristic configurations similar to those
in upstream TensorRT-LLM / CUTLASS for Blackwell, enabling more
performant kernel selection on this new architecture.

title: Extract eh_proj Layer from ParallelLMHead for MTP to Avoid Weight Transposition Issue
body:
When using MTP  and `tie_word_embeddings=true`, unexpected weight transposition behavior may occur.

The specific reason is that the `eh_proj` layer in MTP reuses the `ParallelLMHead` class. When MTP is turned on, its internal judgment logic about `tie_word_embeddings` will cause the `eh_proj` weight to produce unexpected transposition behavior. Therefore, the `eh_proj` layer of MTP is extracted separately to facilitate subsequent development.

title: [LLM] support multi node deploy
body:
## Multi-Machine Deployment

This system supports distributed deployment across multiple nodes. To configure:

### `pod-ips` Parameter
- **Type**: `string`
- **Format**: Comma-separated IPv4 addresses
- **Description**: Specifies all node IPs in the deployment pod
- **Required**: For multi-node deployments only
- **Example**: `"192.168.1.101,192.168.1.102,192.168.1.103"`

### Deployment Workflow
1. **Parameter passing**:
   - Concatenate all node IPs in the deployment cluster
   - Pass as a single string using the `pod-ips` parameter
2. **Unified Node Startup**:
   -  **Same launch command** for all nodes (master and workers)
   - Nodes self-identify roles based on IP position in `pod-ips`
   ```bash

    python fastdeploy.entrypoints.openai.api_server \
    --pod-ips "IP1,IP2,IP3,...,IPN"

### Usage
1.  Only support sending request to the master node （the first ip of the `pod-ips ` parameter)

title: [Stop Sequences] support stop sequences
body:
This PR is to support stop sequences, which is  specific tokens or phrases that signal the model to terminate the current generation process.

## Related environment variables
- `FD_USE_STOP_SEQ`: Whether to use stop sequences, default is 0
- `FD_STOP_SEQS_MAX_LEN `: Maximum length of stop sequences, default is 8
- `FD_MAX_STOP_SEQS_NUM `: Maximum number of stop sequences, default is 5

## Usage
### online serving
```bash 
# launch serving

export FD_USE_STOP_SEQ=1   # set the environment variable to 1
python -m fastdeploy.entrypoints.openai.api_server \
    --model $YOUR_MODEL_PATH \
    --port 8233 \
    --engine-worker-queue-port 8234 \
    --metrics-port 8235 \
    --tensor-parallel-size 1 \
    --max-num-seqs 256 \
    --max-model-len 32768
```

```python
# create a chat request with "stop" parameter
import openai
ip = "0.0.0.0"
service_http_port = "8233"
client = openai.Client(base_url=f"http://{ip}:{service_http_port}/v1", api_key="EMPTY_API_KEY")
response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="default",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": '今天天气真好'},
    ],
    temperature=0.8,
    top_p=0.8,
    stream=False,
    stop=["天气"]
)
```
And response is below, terminating  at the stop sequence: 
```
ChatCompletion(id='chatcmpl-ea74c86a-0ee2-4fa6-bd75-bf2d199fdf2d', choices=[Choice(finish_reason='stop', index=0, logprobs=None, message=ChatCompletionMessage(content='是呀，天气', refusal=None, role='assistant', annotations=None, audio=None, function_call=None, tool_calls=None, reasoning_content=None))], created=1751616717, model='default', object='chat.completion', service_tier=None, system_fingerprint=None, usage=CompletionUsage(completion_tokens=4, prompt_tokens=10, total_tokens=14, completion_tokens_details=None, prompt_tokens_details=PromptTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0)))
```

or give a `stop_token_ids`
```python
import requests

ip = "0.0.0.0"
service_http_port = "8233"    # 服务配置的

api_url = f"http://{ip}:{service_http_port}/v1/chat/completions"
prompt = "今天天气真好"
payload = {
    "messages": [
        {"role": "user", "content": prompt}
    ],
    "temperature": 0.8,
    "top_p": 0,
    "stop_token_ids": [1525, 19770]
}
```
### offline inference
run with `export FD_USE_STOP_SEQ=1`
```
from fastdeploy.engine.sampling_params import SamplingParams
from fastdeploy.entrypoints.llm import LLM

model_name_or_path = YOUR_MODEL_PATH

# give a "stop" parameter
sampling_params = SamplingParams(temperature=0.8, stop=["天气"])
llm = LLM(model=model_name_or_path, tensor_parallel_size=1)
output = llm.generate(prompts="今天天气真好",
                      use_tqdm=True,
                      sampling_params=sampling_params)

print(output)
```
```
[RequestOutput(request_id=d2b70ec7-b232-466e-85d3-e9b379c2a548, prompt='今天天气真好', prompt_token_ids=[3507, 13876, 24034], outputs=CompletionOutput(index=0, send_idx=0, text='，八十岁的奶奶带着三岁的小孙女去公园玩。奶奶牵着小孙女的手，看着周围的花花草草，脸上洋溢着幸福的笑容。\n\n请根据这段描述，写一个关于祖孙俩在公园的温馨故事。\n# 公园里的幸福时光\n天气', token_ids=[93956, 50890, 16844, 13307, 9645, 78778, 4224, 95834, 94344, 94148, 11830, 94642, 93977, 13307, 96602, 92784, 95834, 94344, 13704, 93956, 5556, 11138, 25991, 81489, 95107, 93956, 15082, 89960, 94142, 42396, 27058, 93977, 23, 23, 94515, 2563, 30770, 5434, 93956, 94667, 748, 5175, 95436, 95834, 96415, 94004, 11830, 93964, 30482, 4886, 93977, 23, 93993, 93919, 11830, 5705, 7849, 18272, 23, 13876, 2], draft_token_ids=[], reasoning_content=None, metrics=RequestMetrics(arrival_time=1751617613.0714405, inference_start_time=1751617613.0740652, first_token_time=0.08782720565795898, time_in_queue=0.0013637542724609375, preprocess_cost_time=0.0005915164947509766, model_forward_time=0.8258647918701172, model_execute_time=0.8284895420074463, request_start_time=None)

title: [SOT] Make custom_op dy&st unified
body:
```python
# 文件位置 fastdeploy/model_executor/ops/gpu/fastdeploy_ops.py

@unified
def static_op_extract_text_token_output(max_seq_len,max_seq_len_index,mm_token_num_len,seq_lens_this_time,cu_seqlens_q,score_text):
    # The output variable's dtype use default value 'float32',
    # and the actual dtype of output variable will be inferred in runtime.
    if in_dynamic_or_pir_mode():
        outs = _C_ops._run_custom_op("static_op_extract_text_token_output", max_seq_len,max_seq_len_index,mm_token_num_len,seq_lens_this_time,cu_seqlens_q,score_text)
        res = []
        start_idx = 0
        res.append(outs[start_idx])
        start_idx += 1
        print("static_op_extract_text_token_output op original res is: ", res)
        return res[0] if len(res)==1 else res
```

上述生成的 `static_op_extract_text_token_output` 函数实现中，存在对输出结果根据长度进行解包的逻辑：
当输出结果为单元素列表时，直接返回该元素，否则返回完整的列表。
这种逻辑导致了动态图与静态图模式下接口返回值类型不一致的问题。

在SOT转静执行过程（包括模拟）中，返回值始终经过上述解包处理；
而在动态图模式下，原始实现直接返回底层C++扩展算子的输出，所以我们做进一步处理：

```python
	# 文件位置 fastdeploy/import_ops.py
    @functools.wraps(original_custom_op)
    def unified_op(*args, **kwargs):
        if paddle.in_dynamic_mode():
            res = original_cpp_ext_op(*args, **kwargs)
            if res is None:
                return None
            # TODO(DrRyanHuang): Remove this if when we align the implementation of custom op and C++ extension
            if isinstance(res, list) and len(res) == 1:
                return res[0]
            return res
```

cc @SigureMo
